      "content": "Wait, why Wei Chen specifically for leadership? I thought Jack Sterling's Ivy League background from Yale might make him a more natural fit for the leadership and soft skills side of things in a US-based firm? Also, can you explain why you think an international background like Wei's would better suit the Palo Alto culture compared to, say, Kofi?",
